reviewText: anderson silva demolishing chris leben and rich franklin are the only reasons to watch this dvd. elvis sinosic vs forest griffen was another notable bout. watch, don't buy
I could watch this all day. I love the fact that the UFC puts out these volumes for our entertainment.

...This is the best UFC knockouts DVD so far. I thought 4 was good, but 5 is the UFC's best work to date. Some of the most memorable KO's are on here. 29 fights in all, with top names showcasing their incredible techniques. Lots of Knees!...lol! This DVD is a MUST for any MMA fan or collector. Worth every cent and then some.
